&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;133&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;【 About the company 】&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;156&quot;&gt;At Tomofun, we LOVE pets and technology. Our vision is to bring joy and innovation to every pet lover in the world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;273&quot;&gt;We are pioneers in the pet tech industry. Our debut product, Furbo - the world&#39;s first AIoT treat-tossing pet camera, is the #1 bestseller on Amazon in 15 countries, including the US, UK, and JP and have millions of users in 133 countries. In 2019, we launched an AI-powered subscription service, the Furbo Pet Nanny, which sends smart alerts to our users to notify them to check on the safety of their furbabies when they are home alone. Since the launch of Furbo Pet Nanny, we have saved hundreds of pets&#39; lives and are continuing to innovate and develop new features with our state-of-the-art technology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The learning curve is steep. But the work is exhilarating. Tomofun is on the cusp of a pet-tech boom and we’re looking for smart, innovative thinkers who aspire to incredible things.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;iframe src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/I83Ujp9r_xw&quot; width=&quot;560&quot; height=&quot;314&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;gt; Know more about us:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.furbo.com/&quot;&gt;furbo.com&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/company/tomofun/&quot;&gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https://medium.com/tomofun-tech-blog&quot;&gt;Medium Tech Blog&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;job-preview__description &quot; data-test-description=&quot;&quot;&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;【About the role】&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tomofun 正在尋找一位具備策略思維與創意執行力的「亞太區品牌行銷經理」，你將主導 Furbo 寵物攝影機在台灣、香港、新加坡，及未來擴大東南亞市場的品牌聲量增長，負責社群經營、KOL 與異業合作策略、品牌議題操作等關鍵任務，透過創造高共鳴內容與精準的外部合作，放大品牌影響力並帶動用戶增長與銷售表現。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;如果你熱愛寵物、擅長內容製作與並善於利用社群擴大品牌影響力，相信 Tomofun 是屬於你的舞台，讓你在 AI 浪潮中接觸最新 AI 科技，在國際品牌中發揮影響力！快來加入我們吧～&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;【What you&#39;ll do】&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;區域品牌推廣策略&lt;/strong&gt;：主導台灣、香港、新加坡及未來東南亞市場的品牌推廣規劃，設計行銷節奏並整合各市場資源，以提升品牌知名度、強化品牌好感與用戶信任，間接帶動電商轉換率。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KOL 與跨品牌合作&lt;/strong&gt;：制定 KOL/KOC 合作策略與資源配置，管理並協調當地合作夥伴 (eg. Freelancer, Agency .etc)，確保內容協作與成效最大化；同時開拓跨品牌合作專案，打造雙贏合作模式與破圈聲量。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;社群內容策略&lt;/strong&gt;：規劃各市場的社群平台內容方向與議題操作，提升用戶參與與品牌共鳴；必要時能親自示範高品質內容製作，並引導當地資源或外部團隊進行日常運營。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;數據驅動優化&lt;/strong&gt;：追蹤平台成效與用戶行為，分析各市場內容表現與趨勢，並指導團隊或合作夥伴持續優化，快速因應平台演算法與市場變化。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;跨部門協作&lt;/strong&gt;：與電商、產品、設計、客服等團隊緊密合作，確保品牌推廣與用戶溝通能與銷售轉換、產品定位一致，打造完整品牌體驗。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;【Who you are】&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5 年以上品牌或社群行銷經驗，能從策略規劃到執行落地完整主導專案&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;熟悉多市場運營，具備管理當地團隊/外部合作夥伴的經驗，能協調資源並提升整體效益&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;對社群與 KOL 生態敏感，近半年有實際管理品牌帳號經驗，熟悉 IG、Threads 等平台溝通邏輯&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;具備優秀的內容創意力與審美力，能帶領夥伴共同產出高共鳴內容&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;以數據驅動策略，能清楚轉譯數據為具體優化方向&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;熟悉 CapCut（剪映）、Canva，並善用 AI 工具提升工作效率&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;具備高度自律與時間管理能力，樂於跨部門與跨市場協作&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;中英文流利，能與國際團隊及海外合作對象有效溝通&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;熱愛毛小孩，對寵物產業具備熱情與同理心&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;【 Perks 】&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;能於台灣總部與國際化團隊合作，發揮影響力讓世界都看見！&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;和對科技創新充滿熱情的各領域好手一同合作，相處融洽，彼此腦力激盪，創意無限，一起為毛孩家庭努力！&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;任何人都能自由發表自己的想法，享有充滿信任及資訊透明的扁平化組織。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;每一季舉辦 all-hands meetings，讓全公司成員都能得到關於公司目標、決策的最新資訊，並且開放大家互相交流給予回饋或提問。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;在Tomofun每天都可以帶你的寵物來上班，讓你們時時刻刻都在一起，毛小孩們永遠不寂寞。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tomofun長久以來專注社會公益議題，公司不定期有志工日和服務計畫，歡迎在工作之餘，也可以與我們一同讓世界更好。&

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;133&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;【 About the company 】&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;156&quot;&gt;At Tomofun, we LOVE pets and technology. Our vision is to bring joy and innovation to every pet lover in the world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;273&quot;&gt;We are pioneers in the pet tech industry. Our debut product, Furbo - the world&#39;s first AIoT treat-tossing pet camera, is the #1 bestseller on Amazon in 15 countries, including the US, UK, and JP and have millions of users in 133 countries. In 2019, we launched an AI-powered subscription service, the Furbo Pet Nanny, which sends smart alerts to our users to notify them to check on the safety of their furbabies when they are home alone. Since the launch of Furbo Pet Nanny, we have saved hundreds of pets&#39; lives and are continuing to innovate and develop new features with our state-of-the-art technology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The learning curve is steep. But the work is exhilarating. Tomofun is on the cusp of a pet-tech boom and we’re looking for smart, innovative thinkers who aspire to incredible things.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;iframe src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/I83Ujp9r_xw&quot; width=&quot;560&quot; height=&quot;314&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;gt; Know more about us:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.furbo.com/&quot;&gt;furbo.com&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/company/tomofun/&quot;&gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https://medium.com/tomofun-tech-blog&quot;&gt;Medium Tech Blog&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;*Chat and Email Customer Support (Non-voice)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;【 About the role 】&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The Tomofun Customer Support team cares deeply, genuinely, and passionately about customer needs, striving to provide a world-class support experience that makes our customer-centric company successful.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you will bring a helpful and professional attitude, exhibiting diplomacy, tact, and poise under pressure, as well as a strong sense of curiosity to solve problems. You thrive in an autonomous, fast-paced environment with minimal oversight and enjoy immersing yourself in the culture of Tomofun, the pet tech industry, and the rapidly expanding information technology age.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;(Note: This role starts with a&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;6-month probationary contract designed for your success&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;.&lt;/strong&gt; During this period, you’ll receive hands-on onboarding, coaching, and clear expectations to help you hit your stride. Upon a successful performance review at the 6-month mark, you will transition to a permanent team member with access to our full suite of benefits.)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;【 What you&#39;ll do 】&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Uphold company values by bringing innovation and joy to every pet lover in the world.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effectively resolve customer inquiries with accuracy, empathy, and professionalism.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Articulate and escalate technical issues clearly and concisely to product teams to monitor performance and drive improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Triage incoming requests and identify trends/patterns to proactively flag issues and propose solutions for the rest of the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to the team’s learning and success through mentorship, collaboration, and thorough documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a resilient, customer-focused, and positive attitude in every interaction.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;133&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;【 About the company 】&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;156&quot;&gt;At Tomofun, we LOVE pets and technology. Our vision is to bring joy and innovation to every pet lover in the world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;273&quot;&gt;We are pioneers in the pet tech industry. Our debut product, Furbo - the world&#39;s first AIoT treat-tossing pet camera, is the #1 bestseller on Amazon in 15 countries, including the US, UK, and JP and have millions of users in 133 countries. In 2019, we launched an AI-powered subscription service, the Furbo Pet Nanny, which sends smart alerts to our users to notify them to check on the safety of their furbabies when they are home alone. Since the launch of Furbo Pet Nanny, we have saved hundreds of pets&#39; lives and are continuing to innovate and develop new features with our state-of-the-art technology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The learning curve is steep. But the work is exhilarating. Tomofun is on the cusp of a pet-tech boom and we’re looking for smart, innovative thinkers who aspire to incredible things.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;iframe src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/I83Ujp9r_xw&quot; width=&quot;560&quot; height=&quot;314&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;gt; Know more about us:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.furbo.com/&quot;&gt;furbo.com&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/company/tomofun/&quot;&gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https://medium.com/tomofun-tech-blog&quot;&gt;Medium Tech Blog&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;【About the role】&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;73&quot; data-end=&quot;188&quot;&gt;We are looking for an experienced EE Consultant to serve as a key technical partner across design, quality, and product teams, helping define DQA standards and drive critical electrical design decisions. In this role, you will work closely with internal teams and ODM/CM partners to ensure robust hardware performance from prototype to mass production.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;73&quot; data-end=&quot;188&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;【 Who you are 】&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10+ years of R&amp;amp;D experience in Surveillance or IoT Camera design.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient in power circuitry design with advanced troubleshooting and problem-solving skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep knowledge of EMI / EMC / ESD; capable of risk assessment, design review, and debugging.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience collaborating with ODMs and Contract Manufacturers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to commit ~8 hours per week during the project initiation phase (3-6 months).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;【 What you&#39;ll do 】&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and optimize DQA (Design Quality Assurance) criteria and technical standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead Electrical Design Reviews and drive technical decision-making in discussions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee build stages from P0 through MP:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct internal validation and audit ODM technical reports.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform troubleshooting and propose actionable hardware solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute RMA analysis to identify root causes and preventive measures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;133&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;【 About the company 】&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;156&quot;&gt;At Tomofun, we LOVE pets and technology. Our vision is to bring joy and innovation to every pet lover in the world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;273&quot;&gt;We are pioneers in the pet tech industry. Our debut product, Furbo - the world&#39;s first AIoT treat-tossing pet camera, is the #1 bestseller on Amazon in 15 countries, including the US, UK, and JP and have millions of users in 133 countries. In 2019, we launched an AI-powered subscription service, the Furbo Pet Nanny, which sends smart alerts to our users to notify them to check on the safety of their furbabies when they are home alone. Since the launch of Furbo Pet Nanny, we have saved hundreds of pets&#39; lives and are continuing to innovate and develop new features with our state-of-the-art technology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The learning curve is steep. But the work is exhilarating. Tomofun is on the cusp of a pet-tech boom and we’re looking for smart, innovative thinkers who aspire to incredible things.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;iframe src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/I83Ujp9r_xw&quot; width=&quot;560&quot; height=&quot;314&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;gt; Know more about us:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.furbo.com/&quot;&gt;furbo.com&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/company/tomofun/&quot;&gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https://medium.com/tomofun-tech-blog&quot;&gt;Medium Tech Blog&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;【About the role】&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Imagine giving your pet a belly rub while working from your lap! Furbo is a passionate pet-tech brand dedicated to enhancing the lives of pets through innovation. As the Product Manager for the China market, you will spearhead the strategy and execution of the &lt;strong&gt;Furbo China app,&lt;/strong&gt; driving growth initiatives to optimize the conversion funnel, enhance subscription retention, and leverage cutting-edge AI technologies to maximize user lifetime value.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will translate market research, user data, and insights into actionable product requirements and visionary growth strategies. We are looking for an adaptive, resilient, and open-minded leader eager to explore emerging technologies, including AI integration and intelligent agents. This is a high-impact, hands-on role for an effective communicator who thrives in fast-paced environments. If you are a dog or cat lover, we want to hear from you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;【 What you&#39;ll do 】&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Define Product Strategy and Drive Innovation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the strategy for the Furbo China app by driving product feature development and optimizing subscription user experience to drive growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage cutting-edge technologies, including AI and IoT, to propose user-centric product innovations tailored to the Chinese market.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct in-depth market research and analyze user data to identify key opportunities and craft effective strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Translate User Needs into Exceptional Products&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with users, researchers, and regional teams to gather insights and define clear product requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create user stories and detailed product requirement documents for stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as the SCRUM Product Owner, ensuring timely and high-quality product delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Launch, Monitor, and Optimize&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead cross-functional

