&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with cross-functional teams to design, build, and continuously evolve high-quality Android applications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tackle complex technical challenges and design scalable, maintainable architectures for core app features.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take ownership of key technical decisions, driving architecture, design patterns, and best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor engineers, conduct code reviews, and elevate overall team engineering standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimize performance and reliability in areas such as video streaming, real-time communication, and BLE integration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve app stability, performance, and compatibility across a diverse Android device ecosystem.&lt;/li&gt;
